  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Medicine
Topic:   Blood Types
Formula: ABO system + Rh factor
Note:    Determines blood transfusion compatibility

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Bayes Theorem
Formula: P(A|B) = P(B|A)P(A)/P(B)
Note:    Updating probability based on new evidence

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Wave Equation
Formula: v = fλ
Note:    Speed of wave = frequency × wavelength

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   pH Definition
Formula: pH = -log[H+]
Note:    Measure of hydrogen ion concentration; 7 is neutral

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Gravitational Force
Formula: F = Gm1m2/r²
Note:    Universal gravitation between all masses

============================================================
  ECONOMICS
============================================================

Concept:    Central Bank
Category:   Macroeconomics
Definition: Government institution managing currency, money supply, interest rates
Formula:    Taylor Rule for interest rates
Economist:  John Taylor
Example:    US Federal Reserve raised rates to 5.25% in 2023 to fight inflation

Concept:    Compound Interest
Category:   Finance
Definition: Interest calculated on initial principal and accumulated interest
Formula:    A = P(1 + r/n)^(nt)
Economist:  Various
Example:    Einstein allegedly called it the 8th wonder of the world

Concept:    Gini Coefficient
Category:   Statistics
Definition: Measures income inequality from 0 (equal) to 1 (one person has all)
Formula:    G = 1 - 2∫L(x)dx
Economist:  Corrado Gini
Example:    USA Gini ~0.41; Denmark ~0.29; South Africa ~0.63

